prompts.frontCover: Flat 2D illustration for a birthday card, dreamy fantasy art style. A fluffy, slightly grumpy-looking alpaca wearing a ridiculously small, glittering party hat perched between its ears, is floating serenely on a giant, iridescent soap bubble. The bubble drifts through a magical, pastel-hued twilight sky filled with soft, glowing clouds in shades of lavender, peach, and mint green. Tiny, sparkling fireflies and whimsical floating flower petals surround the alpaca. Below, a charming landscape of rolling, cotton-candy-like hills is dotted with tiny, glowing mushrooms. The alpaca has a comical expression of mild annoyance, as if being magically floated for its birthday is a slight inconvenience. In the center, written in a beautiful, readable, elegant cursive script, is the text "Hope your birthday is unbelieva-bubble!". The overall aesthetic is ethereal, whimsical, and humorous, with a soft, magical glow.
